# Privacy Policy for Archibald (Automod)

**Last Updated: June 7, 2025**

## 1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how Archibald (Automod) ("the Bot", "we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects information when you use our Discord bot.

## 2. Information We Collect

### 2.1 Automatically Collected Information
When you use the Bot, we may collect:
- Discord user IDs
- Discord server (guild) IDs
- Message content (only when directly interacting with the Bot or when necessary for moderation features)
- Command usage data
- Server configuration settings

### 2.2 Stored Information
The Bot may store:
- Server-specific configuration settings
- Moderation logs (user actions, infractions)
- Custom command configurations
- Role and permission settings
- Temporary cache data for Bot functionality

## 3. How We Use Information

We use collected information to:
- Provide and maintain Bot functionality
- Execute commands and features as requested
- Maintain moderation logs and server security
- Improve Bot performance and features
- Troubleshoot technical issues
- Ensure compliance with our Terms of Service

## 4. Data Storage and Security

- Data is stored on secure servers with access limited to Bot operators
- We implement reasonable security measures to protect stored data
- Cached data is automatically purged after a reasonable time period
- We do not sell, trade, or transfer your information to third parties

## 5. Data Retention

- Server configuration data is retained as long as the Bot remains in your server
- Moderation logs are retained for 90 days unless otherwise configured
- Temporary cache data is retained for no more than 24 hours
- You may request deletion of your server's data at any time

## 6. User Rights

You have the right to:
- Request access to data we store about your server
- Request correction of inaccurate data
- Request deletion of your server's data
- Remove the Bot from your server at any time

## 7. Third-Party Services

The Bot may integrate with:
- Discord API (governed by Discord's Privacy Policy)
- Gaming APIs for stats and information (if applicable)
- Other third-party services as disclosed in Bot documentation

## 8. Children's Privacy

The Bot is not intended for use by anyone under the age of 13, consistent with Discord's minimum age requirement.

## 9. International Data

Data may be processed and stored in various locations. By using the Bot, you consent to the transfer of information to countries outside your country of residence.

## 10. Changes to Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes.

## 11. Contact Information

For privacy-related questions or concerns, please contact us through our community Discord server.

## 12. Data Breach Notification

In the event of a data breach that may compromise user information, we will:
- Notify affected server administrators through Discord
- Post an announcement in our community server
- Take immediate steps to secure the affected data

---

**By using Archibald (Automod), you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to this Privacy Policy.**
